<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-11-14T15:50:45-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-11-14T15:50:45-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T15:50:45-05:00</updated><title> TikTok 将 Getty Images 插入其人工智能生成的广告和头像中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;TikTok 徽标的矢量艺术。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZVodkScKVxTqVABgXF35o3lud1k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73723835/STK051_TIKTOK_CVirginia_C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OHfva2&quot;>;TikTok 将让广告商&lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.gettyimages.com/en/getty-images/getty- images-unlocks-premium-creative-content-for-tiktok-advertisers&quot;>;使用平台的人工智能广告制作工具时从 Getty Images 提取内容&lt;/a>;。通过集成，广告商可以使用 Getty 的许可图像和视频来制作包含人工智能生成内容的广告，包括看起来像真人的人工智能头像。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Gjx6ND&quot;>;集成将通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/17/24179971/tiktok-ads-ai- generated-avatars-creators-language-dubbing&quot;>;TikTok 的 Symphony Creative Studio&lt;/a>; — 一个 AI-动力视频生成工具&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296429/more-ai- generated-ads-are-coming-to-tiktok&quot;>;今天向所有人推出广告商&lt;/a>;。该工具可以根据产品描述生成视频，添加人工智能头像来“谈论”产品，甚至可以采用不同语言的人工智能配音。广告商还可以使用该工具生成广告的多个版本，以及“重新混合”现有广告。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;GIF：TikTok&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption >;&lt;em>;T...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296636/tiktok-ai- ads-getty-images-content&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296636/tiktok-ai-ads-getty-images-content" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com